title: Tuesday Post Show (6-8-21)

description:
Eddie talks about seeing 2 near death experiences go down recently. They are both pretty crazy! Bobby talks about how he realized he met another Billionaire, the face tattoo trend and Tinder launching a block your ex-tool. Bobby also gets an update from Morgan2 about her new boyfriend. We learned a few details about him that she will share. We also even give him a new name. We also played a game we didn’t get to last week about Famous TV Characters.
